			(property "Description" "Normally closed solder jumper (1 of 2 connections)\n\nThis jumper has an aperture in the stencil to allow solder paste to bridge one of the two connections. One connection is normally closed (NC), while the other is normally open (NO). Wick off the solder to open the connection. Reapply solder to reclose the connection. Apply solder to the other side instead to change the current path."
