			(property "Description" "WS2813C-2020 is an intelligent control LED light source, its exterior adopts the latest MOLDING packaging technology, the control circuit and RGB chips are integrated in a package of 2020 component. Its internal includes intelligent digital port data latch and signal reshaping amplification drive circuit. Also include a precision internal oscillator and a voltage programmable constant current control part, effectively ensuring the pixel point light color height consistent.\n\nSource: https://www.tme.eu/Document/347c7b90c44c0358b951bb80c06ea839/WS2813C-2020.pdf  Datasheet"
